# ByteRun Protector for PHP Decoder
## Why did you create this?
There are other tools out there that do the same thing:
- https://www.unphp.net/
- http://lombokcyber.com/en/detools/decode-byterun

While this is true, sometimes you don’t want to submit the data you have to a web service. In these cases, you can run this php script on your local machine.

## How do I use it?
Just point this script at your ByteRun “protected” file and hit enter.

```
./byterun_decoder.php index.php
```

### Example

```
# cat example.php
<?php
$_F=__FILE__;
```
